name: Fatigued Sprints
description:
There are two purposes of todays tough session. The first is a fatigued sprint, including a series of intervals designed to load your legs, work your sustainable powers, but ultimately, to soften you up for what is to come. The second is a double sprint, simulating a more true sprint scenario. You will often need to sprint to fight for position prior to launching your race winning move. Enjoy!
